These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
City: london, boston, marseilles
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, car, train
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, bellflower
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the train and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the designer is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| City   | boston        | marseilles    | london       |
| Transport   | car     | scooter  | train       |
| Flower         | amaryllis     | daisy | bellflower |

