.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
City: nizza, san-francisco, prague
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, rock-climbing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, siglo
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| City   | prague      | san-francisco   | nizza    |
| Hobby           | video-games        | rock-climbing      | collecting         |
| Cigar         | blend | baccarat  | siglo |

