.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
City: london, colone, venice
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
House: cape-cod, victorian, farmhouse
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, june, september
 1. the person traveling to colone is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the farmhouse house is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the victorian house and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the victorian house is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the victorian house is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| City          | venice      | colone      | london      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | satire    | spy          |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | folk      | r&b          |
| House   | victorian    | cape-cod  | farmhouse      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Birthday         | august  | june   | september     |

