The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, fishing, sudoku
3 different games are played: whist, chess, go
House: craftsman, palace, cape-cod
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, pop
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, mango, pepper
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating pepper##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the palace house and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person playing whist is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person playing whist and the person playing go##2
10. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk           | soy-milk      |
| Hobby         | chess       | sudoku         | fishing       |
| Game           | whist    | chess | go |
