The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, azure
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, journalist, mechanic
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of salsa is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the doctor##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Music-Genre         | techno     | gospel     | salsa  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Color   | green  | azure     | aquamarine |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Job         | doctor    | mechanic | journalist   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

