There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, american, brazilian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros, swisher
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, victorian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the american is between the person drinking fanta and the old-henry-smoker##2
6. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the victorian house##1
9. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Nationality          | argentine     | american      | brazilian     |
| Cigar         | oliveros | swisher    | old-henry      |
| House   | gothic-revival   | cape-cod | victorian    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Sport         | cricket     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |
| Transport     | scooter     | ship       | motorbike    |

