.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina, davidoff
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, may, november
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
City: edinburgh, nizza, new-york
1. the havana-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the davidoff-smoker and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the person traveling to edinburgh##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | vegafina    | havana       | davidoff      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Birthday           | may  | july | november    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| City     | nizza    | new-york     | edinburgh      |

 